name: Welcome to Web3: Token 004
description:
Your new social networks — it's time to introduce you to a few new tools: Discord and Twitter. Both will take some getting used to but will help you discover new artists and projects, as well as engage with the NFT and collector community in a more meaningful way. 

Discord is a comprehensive chat, typically organised by project. For example, @JJJJJJohn has his own discord channel with all his projects and community members are admins. 

Twitter is a great tool to find artists and projects you might be interested in. You can search #tags of nearly anything and start diving down rabbit holes commitment free.
